(122, 'admin', 'ALL_DEPT,', '奖励通知', '<div><span style="font-size: x-small; font-family: Verdana;">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt -0.1pt; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: center; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: -.01gd; mso-layout-grid-align: none;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN;">关于对郭毅萌和</span><span style="font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体;">刘新雨进行奖励的通知<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt -0.1pt; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: center; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: -.01gd; mso-layout-grid-align: none;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt -0.1pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: -.01gd; mso-layout-grid-align: none;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">前不久，北京综合信息网开展线上运营推广活动，当公司正为客户准备线下礼品而忙碌时，产品部的同事郭毅萌主动联系到20张免费滑雪券无偿献给公司，从而更加丰富了公司此次活动的奖品。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">与此同时，丰台支公司的刘新雨主动联系到</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">广东卫视</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;" lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">8mm</span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">栏目组来我司进行实地拍摄情景剧。广东卫视作为省级电视台在全国有着广泛的影响力和收视率，无形中对我司提高宣传度、扩大影响力起了积极的作用。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;" lang="EN-US"></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">为此公司决定依据《金凯通达员工奖惩管理制度》给以两位同事现金奖励</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;" lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">,</span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">感谢他们为公司做出的贡献。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">郭毅萌和</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">刘新雨</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">这种具有高度主人翁意识是我们金凯通达每位员工都应该学习的榜样，也希望其他同事在工作过程中发挥所长，群策群力，发扬主人翁精神,</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">为公司的长远发展做出自己的贡献。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;" lang="EN-US"></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 228pt; line-height: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 19.0;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;" lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 228pt; line-height: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 19.0;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;" lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 228pt; line-height: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 19.0;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;" lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 228pt; line-height: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 19.0;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 金凯通达（北京）国际投资有限公司</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;" lang="EN-US"></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 300pt; line-height: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 25.0;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;